Date: Sun, 22 Jun 2025 16:41:53 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 169/194] ASoC: codecs: Add support for TAS2557 codec

driver is reworked from the official android driver and probably requires additional clean up

tas2557 itself is very similar to tas2559

Signed-off-by: Mihail Maksimov <miha5424@gmail.com>
